TextEng: Who are you? What do you do?
Who is you? What you do?
You wish a password?
You want password?
Can I ask about the Tavern and what's below it?
Text: 선술집이랑 그 아래에 뭐가 있는지 물어봐도 될까?

TextEng: Me maybe ask about Tavern and what's under it?
Text: 나 선술집이랑 밑에 뭐 있는지 물어봐도 돼?

TextEng: The password is "Cornerstone."
Password is "Cornerstone," or something.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> If you don't care, how about just forgetting it?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 상관없다면 그냥 없던 일로 해 주지 않겠어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> If you think this silly, how about we just forget it?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 바보 같은 일이라 생각하면, 그냥 잊자. 어때?

TextEng: Well, handsome, maybe we can... work something out?
Text: 저기, 멋진 분. 어쩌면 우리... 뭔가 합의를 볼 수 있지 않을까?

TextEng: Aw, come on handsome. Pretty please let me through?
Text: 아, 제발 멋진 분. 제발 부탁이에요, 통과시켜 주세요?

TextEng: Goodbye.
Will some gold make you forget you need a password?
Text: 금화 좀 주면 암호가 필요하다는 걸 잊어줄래?

TextEng: Maybe you take gold and forget you need password?
Text: 금화 받고 암호 필요하다는 거 잊어줄래?

TextEng: You'll let me pass or I'll feed you your spine!
Text: 길을 비켜. 아니면 네 척추를 뽑아 먹여 주지!

TextEng: You let me pass or me kill you!
Text: 길 비켜. 아니면 나 너 죽여!

TextEng: I don't know the password.
Me not know password.
How about 50 gold to look the other way?
You take 50 gold to forget me?
How about 100 gold to look the other way?
You take 100 gold to forget me?
200 gold should get you to forget me, hmm?
Text: 금화 200개면 나를 잊어줄 수 있지, 응?

TextEng: You forget me for 200 gold, maybe?
I was only testing. I meant nothing by it.
Text: 그냥 시험해 본 거야. 별 뜻은 없었어.

TextEng: Me just kidding. Me a kidder.
